{"tid":2024951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"奶茶聯盟最新動向（反水壩白宮聯署加抵制破壞言論自由嘅Krispy Kreme）","createTime":"2020-05-20T02:38:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T07:49:20.000Z","uid":246588,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"337fc69dd913669c66157087c9c1621199062384","tid":2024951,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"咁多位手足重記唔記得我地同泰國、台灣結盟做奶茶聯盟，宜家奶茶聯盟又有新動向<br />\n<br />\n1. 反對中國係湄公河上游起水壩嘅白宮聯署<br />\n聯署已經唔夠數而失敗，但係之後又有人重新發起過聯署，目前已經有2.2萬人簽咗，大家幫手簽同share<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-china-build-dam-upstream-mekong-river-0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fstop-china-build-dam-upstream-mekong-river-0&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7sVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=b4590760\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/stop-china-build-dam-upstream-mekong-river-0</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 抵制破壞言論自由嘅Krispy Kreme<br />\n<br />\n早前因為Krispy Kreme嘅泰國員工因為網上言論而被炒，成個泰國D網民話要抵制Krispy Kreme，經常分享其他賣droughts嘅商店，玩殘Krispy Kreme，佢地希望我地同台灣人幫手抵制當地Krispy Kreme<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/PhilosophyNook/status/1262608946361032707?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPhilosophyNook%2Fstatus%2F1262608946361032707%3Fs%3D09&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7sVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=3b807a4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPhilosophyNook%2Fstatus%2F1262608946361032707%3Fs%3D09&h=cc6987fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/PhilosophyNook/status/1262608946361032707?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Khunprinx/status/1262374367859822592?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKhunprinx%2Fstatus%2F1262374367859822592%3Fs%3D09&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7sVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=ebaa3e7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FKhunprinx%2Fstatus%2F1262374367859822592%3Fs%3D09&h=a5fd324d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Khunprinx/status/1262374367859822592?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n我自己上網睇過，香港宜家無Krispy Kreme分店，但係台灣就有7間Krispy Kreme分店。<br />\n<br />\n所以我地可以盡量傳信息比台灣人，希望佢地幫手抵制台灣Krispy Kreme，或者去泰國Krispy Kreme Facebook專頁派嬲加留言<br />\n<br />\n重有，最重要嘅係要留意Twitter戰線，未加入嘅快D加入<br />\n<br />\n煲底見<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"5a5f4049fae1e0685809b156ea0f8f7b75b78253","tid":2024951,"uid":246588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:38:42.000Z","msg":"推1次，光復香港近1步"},{"pid":"7865fc30d6c7b71e7e8b80175f56460a169fbe2a","tid":2024951,"uid":243612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:42:28.000Z","msg":"推！國際陣線！"},{"pid":"71f99f82af655c2d6aa1e27ec5bbc24bb2084af3","tid":2024951,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T02:45:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d84dd4c5824dca6475dd1e5cfcdafaad4d76ed7c","tid":2024951,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T03:00:01.000Z","msg":"已簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ee2a0ad57b9275fd2b69b91c9592577ca7340ba","tid":2024951,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"簽左<br />\n<br />\n推"},{"pid":"6eee3237243cd0c407bbc7c139bebab6f258f915","tid":2024951,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"21d8f5bdade49d59bebee361e6bb04ea26b574a0","tid":2024951,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"Signed"},{"pid":"9dea456e96988cac13d5161ba2ea2a1df2436466","tid":2024951,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T17:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p