，簡單直接嘅英文就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c54fc9c0a488a6d5ae3ac90d14c462b5f81da7","tid":2024951,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:44:36.000Z","msg":"3. 壞消息，因為Twitter修改條款，損害泰國人言論自由，有泰國用户要刪除帳戶，改去Minds繼續<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taL3Ev8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtaL3Ev8.jpg&h=5cfb6242&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XnXd1Ku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXnXd1Ku.jpg&h=50c595fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a3e35edb3e9d5cf80cd8117a3133e907eb8443a","tid":2024951,"uid":80303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:49:20.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}